  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DenScreen
    GUI screen for the power up den in each city.
    DiceRollScreen
    GUI screen for playing a minigame vs the city villain.
    EnterCityScreen
    GUI screen which displays info about the next city the user will enter.
    GuessNumberScreen
    GUI screen which enables the user to play a number guessing game against the city villain.
    HeroSelectScreen
    GUI screen for choosing which heroes the user wishes to have in their team.
    HomeBaseScreen
    GUI screen for the home base of a city.
    HospitalScreen
    GUI screen for a hospital where the user can apply healing items to their heroes.
    LairScreen
    GUI screen for the entrance to the villain's lair.
    PaperScissorsRockScreen
    GUI screen for the paper-scissors-rock game the user plays against the villain.
    SetupScreen
    GUI screen for setting up the game.
    ShopScreen
    GUI screen for the game's shop.
    VillainsScreen
    GUI screen for battling the villain.
